There are currently 116 classrooms assigned for general use. Classrooms include Campus Lecture Halls lecture halls and the smaller rooms in which small lectures and discussion sessions are held.  See also Campus Buildings for information on buildings and the largest lecture halls.

For a list of all classrooms at UC Davis and what they contain (including types of seating, whether they have projectors, internet access, DVD players, etc), visit the http://registrar.ucdavis.edu/schedule/html/sum_display.cfm registrar page.
